description:
Foundation of EMPI B-School, in green pollution free surroundings in South Delhi with its unique 24x7 learning environment, conceptualized by Psychologist Pankaj (now Vice President), was laid by EMPI Patron Chairman Ajit N. Haksar (Chairman Emeritus ITC Ltd.) in 1995. Commencing with its flagship AICTE approved PG level Programme in Business Management, conducted under the direction of former Director BHEL & Sr. Management consultant (Commonwealth, UK) Mr. Gurnam Saran (now President) & Expert Advisory Body Chairman Mr. P. S. Bami, EMPI has added specialized intense industry interactive PG level Professional Programmes. Their curriculum are crafted under expert guidance of India's icons and delivered through its Centers of Excellence (CoEs) chaired by Ms. Tara Sinha, Dr. D. V. Kapur, Dr. Udai Pareek and Mr. N. Vittal lAS (Retd). All Programmes are 2-Years Full time residential and lead to award of AICTE approved PG Diploma in Management.

The 2 year full time PGDM Specialisations conducted as per the approval of AICTE and in collaboration with MNCs:

1) PGDM (Research & Business Analytics){in association with IBM co-certified Business Analytics}
2) PGDM (Advertising Communication) {in association with IBM co-certified Digital and Social Media Marketing}
3) PGDM (Global Business) {in association with IBM co-certified E-Commerce}
4) PGDM (Human Resource) {in association with ManpowerGroup}
5) PGDM (Smart Cities and Facility Management) {in association with JLL}
6) PGDM (Renewable Energy Management) {with scholarships from SkypowerGlobal}
7) PGDM (General Management) {Marketing and Finance}

In addition to the PGDM Programmes, EMPI also provides 1 year Fast Track MNC Co-Certified, Futuristic PGPs as per the Train to Hire MNC Model with 100% Job Assurance. The programmes have flexibility of weekend coursework for working executives.

Visit us at: www.empi.ac.in
